formulas.name: calc_booking_date_v1
default_renewal_risk
formulas.expression: IF( {!$Record.RecordType.Name} = "Renewal" && ISPICKVAL({!$Record.Renewal_Risk__c},"") && NOT(ISPICKVAL({!$Record.Type},"PIlot")) && {!$Record.IsClosed} = FALSE, "Expected to renew", TEXT({!$Record.Renewal_Risk__c}) )

formulas.name: Did_regress_stage
formulas.expression: IF( {!$Record.IsClosed}, FALSE, IF( VALUE(MID(TEXT({!$Record.StageName}), 2, 1)) < VALUE(MID(TEXT({!$Record__Prior.StageName}), 2, 1)), TRUE, FALSE ) )

formulas.name: opportunity_team
formulas.expression: "("&{!$Record.Owner.User_Role_Short_Name__c}&") " & {!$Record.Owner.FirstName} & " " & {!$Record.Owner.LastName} & BR() & IF( NOT({!$Record.IsClosed}) && ISPICKVAL({!$Record.StageName},"(1) Qualification") && {!$Record.OwnerId}<>{!$Record.Sales_Qualified_By__c}, IF(ISBLANK({!$Record.Sales_Qualified_By__c}),"","("&{!$Record.Sales_Qualified_By__r.User_Role_Short_Name__c}&") " &{!$Record.Sales_Qualified_By__r.FirstName}& " " & {!$Record.Sales_Qualified_By__r.LastName} & BR()), NULL ) & IF(ISBLANK({!$Record.Technical_Account_Manager__c}),"","("&{!$Record.Technical_Account_Manager__r.User_Role_Short_Name__c}&") " &{!$Record.Technical_Account_Manager__r.FirstName}& " " & {!$Record.Technical_Account_Manager__r.LastName} & BR()) & IF(ISBLANK({!$Record.Sales_Engineer__c}),"","("&{!$Record.Sales_Engineer__r.User_Role_Short_Name__c}&") " &{!$Record.Sales_Engineer__r.FirstName}& " " & {!$Record.Sales_Engineer__r.LastName} & BR()) & IF(ISBLANK({!$Record.Executive_Sponsor__c}),"","("&{!$Record.Executive_Sponsor__r.User_Role_Short_Name__c}&") " &{!$Record.Executive_Sponsor__r.FirstName}& " " & {!$Record.Executive_Sponsor__r.LastName})

formulas.name: Standardized_Opp_Name
formulas.expression: CASE({!$Record.Booking_Type__c}, "Debook","DEBOOK ", "Putback","PUTBACK ", "" )& {!name_entity_prefix} & IF(ISBLANK({!$Record.BU_Name__c}),""," ("&{!$Record.BU_Name__c}&")") & " - " & IF(ISBLANK({!Get_booking_setting.Opportunity_Short_Name__c}),"Unknown",{!Get_booking_setting.Opportunity_Short_Name__c}) & " " & IF( {!$Record.RecordType.Name} = "Renewal" && NOT(ISBLANK({!$Record.Term_Start_Date__c})), TEXT(MONTH( {!$Record.Term_Start_Date__c} )) & "/" & TEXT(YEAR({!$Record.Term_Start_Date__c})), TEXT(MONTH({!$Record.CloseDate} )) & "/" & TEXT(YEAR({!$Record.CloseDate})) )
